{"tid":1783003,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人仲有幾多個5年","createTime":"2019-12-14T12:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T12:38:54.000Z","uid":8410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90fd68c19c4f0c57291425ac8481ebbebb797199","tid":1783003,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"大家睇下新聞都知中國對香港態度就明白將來有幾兇險。但依家俾我的感覺係運動已經完了<br />\n<br />\n2014 雨傘運動至5年後的2019 反送中，直到依家， 見証住運動的衰亡。 大家已經back to normal , 出去飲飲食食， 去激安排隊。 已經唔會再諗行動， 點救被捉的人。 香港人點對得住2014 至2019 為香港犧牲的人。 已經唔會再有多個5年俾你進化俾你浪費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f8Vu2iu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff8Vu2iu.jpg&h=589eb556&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e37294f27fd48455043d17ec68e6062cca4c2174","tid":1783003,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7d129b2c44073ed42e637eefe614613ccc7abb","tid":1783003,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccf38ba278148a57111aa35663fb4c606884cdc","tid":1783003,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:19:49.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0858e39187d6ae3e11cb82dccbb8b76cb0fcff23","tid":1783003,"uid":313716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:21:31.000Z","msg":"別灰心<br />\n星星之火 早已燎原"},{"pid":"a577c688a5fc87fefc839786a487d326e8b79569","tid":1783003,"uid":227851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:23